# .dockerignore for polytrader (security hygiene for L2 key + build context)
# Addresses high-severity review finding (build context exposure of .env* containing POLYMARKET_PRIVATE_KEY during docker build COPY . .)
# Standard for secret hygiene in Dockerfile flows with k8s-set-l2-key (which relies on .env.local on build host).

.env*
.env.local
.env.*.local
target/
**/.git
**/.gitattributes
**/.gitignore
*.pem
wallet*.json
**/.env*
**/*.key
**/*.secret
**/secrets/
# Keep Cargo.lock etc for reproducible builds; exclude only sensitive
# Note: .dockerignore does not affect k8s secret mounts (runtime only) or git (already ignored)
